                        To unpause, just press "run" button. While <strong>reset</strong> will allow you to clear best path and visited nodes.
                        </p>
                        <p></p>
                        <h5 class="modal-subtitle">Special Nodes</h5>
                        <p> Remember that you can interact with <strong>special nodes</strong> before ,during, and after pathfinding (except during <strong>maze generation</strong>).
                        If nodes have been visited or a path is already displayed, the algorithm will <strong>recalculate in real time</strong> as you move objects.</p>
